about.summary: Autologging makes logging and tracing Python classes easy.

name: autologging
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "Autologging" %}
{% set version = "1.3.2" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.zip"
  sha256: "117659584d8aab8cf62046f682f8e57b54d958b8571c737fa8bf15c32937fbb6"

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - autologging

about:
  home: "http://ninthtest.info/python-autologging/"
  license: "MIT"
  license_family: "MIT"
  license_file: "LICENSE.txt"
  summary: "Autologging makes logging and tracing Python classes easy."
  doc_url: "http://ninthtest.info/python-autologging/index.html"
  dev_url: "https://github.com/mzipay/Autologging"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - notestaff
